## **Troubleshooting**

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| `gh auth status` invalid token | `gh auth login` |
| `gh repo create` auth error after create | `git remote add origin ...` + `git push -u origin main` |
| SSL certificate error on push | One-time `$env:GIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY='true'` (see [git_local_push.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/git_local_push.mdc)) |
| Repo name already exists | Use existing remote or pick a new name |
| Secret file staged | `git restore --staged <path>`, add to `.gitignore`, recommit |
| `.idea/` or `node_modules/` staged | Add to `.gitignore`, `git rm -r --cached` if needed |

